   "text": "We'll check off that list for those of you."
  },
  {
   "start": 437.29,
   "end": 438.29,
   "text": "Probably if not bad at your best."
  },
  {
   "start": 438.29,
   "end": 439.29,
   "text": "We have to do one again."
  },
  {
   "start": 439.29,
   "end": 440.69,
   "text": "If you leave your life."
  },
  {
   "start": 440.79,
   "end": 442.29,
   "text": "It's not going home."
